Date: Wed, 8 Jul 2026 03:20:46 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] Redesign hero + fix splash/disclaimer contrast and video
 loop

Hero:
- Ping-pong background video (plays forward then reverses via a new
  HeroVideo component) so the loop never snaps; object-position centred
  so the brand mark in the footage isn't cropped to a corner.
- Replace the FoundersCard-style cream 'Preview membership' pill with
  InScape-branded CTAs: an orange gradient 'Become a member' primary and
  a glass 'Explore campaigns' secondary, a glass eyebrow tag, a
  'start free with 3 Credits' trust line, and a vignette for depth.

Contrast fixes:
- IntroSplash is now a theme-independent dark brand reveal, so the
  'Welcome, {name}' line stays visible in light mode (was white on cream).
- Campaign-detail join disclaimer uses a readable text tone (was near
  invisible ghost text on the gradient card).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
