Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Fix glitchy hero video: seamless crossfade loop instead
 of reverse-seek ping-pong

The ping-pong loop reverse-seeked the video every frame, which stutters
because MP4 only decodes cleanly from keyframes. Replace it with two
stacked copies that crossfade at the loop point, so the loop is smooth
with no seeking. Respects reduced motion.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_01XAoaVu96SZ2QScyEZx2iY8
